
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>
      Demande approuvée
    </title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #EDEAE4; font-family: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"
  >

    <table
      role="presentation"
      width="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      style="background-color: #EDEAE4; padding: 48px 20px;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table
            role="presentation"
            width="580"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="max-width: 580px; width: 100%;"
          >

            <!-- Brand Header -->
            <tr>
              <td style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 36px;">
                <span style="font-size: 22px; color: #1C1917; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">{{ brandName }}</span>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Main Card -->
            <tr>
              <td
                style="background-color: #FDFCFB; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #E8E3DC;"
              >

                <!-- Top accent line -->
                <div style="height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1C1917 0%, #44403C 50%, #A8A29E 100%);">
                </div>

                <!-- Success Header -->
                <div style="padding: 48px 56px 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F0EDE8;">
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="vertical-align: middle; width: 52px;">
                        <div
                          style="width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #DCFCE7; border: 1.5px solid #BBF7D0; text-align: center; line-height: 44px; font-size: 18px;"
                        >
                          ✓
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <td style="vertical-align: middle; padding-left: 16px;">
                        <p
                          style="margin: 0 0 2px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6B7280;"
                        >
                          Statut
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 26px; color: #1C1917; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">
                          Demande approuvée
                        </p>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </div>

                <!-- Body -->
                <div style="padding: 40px 56px;">

                  <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #44403C; font-weight: 300;">
                    Bonjour <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917;">{{ userName }}</span>,
                  </p>

                  <p style="margin: 0 0 28px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; color: #57534E; font-weight: 300;">
                    Votre demande d'accès à la plateforme <span style="font-weight: 500; color: #1C1917;">{{ brandName }} </span>a été examinée et <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #16A34A;">approuvée</span>. Pour finaliser l'activation de votre compte, nous vous invitons à définir votre mot de passe à l'aide du lien ci-dessous.
                  </p>

                  <!-- Divider -->
                  <div style="height: 1px; background-color: #F0EDE8; margin-bottom: 32px;">
                  </div>

                  <!-- CTA -->
                  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;">
                    <a
                      href="{{ setPasswordUrl }}"
                      style="display: inline-block; padding: 15px 40px; background-color: #1C1917; color: #FDFCFB; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"
                    >
                      Définir mon mot de passe →
                    </a>
                  </div>

                  <!-- Expiry notice -->
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td
                        style="background-color: #FEFCE8; border: 1px solid #FDE68A; border-radius: 4px; padding: 14px 18px;"
                      >
                        <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                          <tr>
                            <td style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: #78350F; font-weight: 300;">
                              Ce lien est valable <strong style="font-weight: 600;">72 heures </strong>à compter de la réception de cet e-mail. Passé ce délai, vous devrez soumettre une nouvelle demande d'accès.
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                </div>

              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 32px 20px 0;">
                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="border-top: 1px solid #D6D3CD; padding-top: 24px; text-align: center;">
                      <p style="margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 12.5px; color: #A8A29E; font-weight: 300;">
                        Pour toute question, veuillez contacter l'administrateur de la plateforme.
                      </p>
                      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #C4BFB8; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">
                        {{ new Date().getFullYear() }} · {{ brandName }} · Tous droits réservés
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

  </body>
</html>
